Class org.lzo.Int 

java.lang.Object
   |
   +----java.lang.Number
           |
           +----org.lzo.Int
public class Int
extends Number
The Int class wraps a value of the primititve type int in an object. As opposed to java.lang.Integer the value can be modified after the object has been created.
